{"tid":1149373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<急！><我認我柒> 特區護照爛左！求補領過程實例","createTime":"2019-05-11T06:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T04:57:17.000Z","uid":205193,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3438b778c54582a6cdcac049f85c794469e5c6","tid":1149373,"uid":205193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:14:53.000Z","msg":"9號屋企開party, 比姪仔姪女剪爛左本護照！！<br />\n10號去左灣仔一次，拎少左本屍骸去，今日5月11號去整返，話要等4至6個星期，想6月5號之前拎。但當時比個姨姨嚇9我，唔記得問有無得快啲拎。<br />\n有無人有經驗幾耐拎到？上網好多都係唔見護照就唔洗一個月，爛左係咪會再快啲？？<br />\nBNO 既答案先多謝分享，唔諗住，啲咁珍貴既證明文件要認真搞，加上一次性既幫我唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673c6189b14d37bf1eaee622a9ffa1cdfa19bd01","tid":1149373,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:39:18.000Z","msg":"easy la"},{"pid":"60e5653b88908cb53c558fc937945bc232ca38dd","tid":1149373,"uid":205193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"673c6189b14d37bf1eaee622a9ffa1cdfa19bd01","tid":1149373,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:39:18.000Z","msg":"easy la"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:40:54.000Z","msg":"有幾easy???"},{"pid":"7fde6ac7438cb1bd5809faf9a384f8bb9288737b","tid":1149373,"uid":9694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"晨早走返去問下班櫃檯廢老啦<br />\n廢老都兇到你，你又斯斯然返屋企上連登問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73140c66005f72d92bb309e4ed74f354d91daa2","tid":1149373,"uid":224278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:28:51.000Z","msg":"第一 你本護照爛成點 有無缺頁<br />\n<br />\n第二 點解你需要6月5日就拎"},{"pid":"e3e44e8e32db908708c05b5aaa5e6c3f3ec7740b","tid":1149373,"uid":188849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:30:38.000Z","msg":"講真，如果你有本舊BNO其實唔麻煩<br />\n三個星期內應該收到新護照<br />\n你最多要搵日副簽<br />\n依家連相都可以電子Upload<br />\n『薪火post』BNO 續期資訊(35) 一理通百理明，明白了續期可變簡單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1130067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1130067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"017cafc9547e4aa3fc2d01c1950ce095328e95c1","tid":1149373,"uid":44512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"上年唔見左本護照，過一個月多d 左右就要去旅行，去到櫃台同佢講可唔可以快證，佢話要寫低原因，然後話要等d 呀sir 決定。"},{"pid":"34a4c610bd026b7c890905fe482714f1a6540344","tid":1149373,"uid":44512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"017cafc9547e4aa3fc2d01c1950ce095328e95c1","tid":1149373,"uid":44512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"上年唔見左本護照，過一個月多d 左右就要去旅行，去到櫃台同佢講可唔可以快證，佢話要寫低原因，然後話要等d 呀sir 決定。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"同埋一定要係灣仔拎"},{"pid":"81c589ec1abe54b5beceb8f515b6ea3458fb4220","tid":1149373,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"成個月驚乜鳩 整本新都拎到啦"},{"pid":"0a2b34c9296fff8a5a51ac1515ebbacbdd4c6253","tid":1149373,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T12:05:54.000Z","msg":"你阿哥/細佬果邊都幾有家教喎 護照都可以剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94881de5938b62be7fcb90b947d354934474adf","tid":1149373,"uid":205193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b73140c66005f72d92bb309e4ed74f354d91daa2","tid":1149373,"uid":224278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:28:51.000Z","msg":"第一 你本護照爛成點 有無缺頁<br />\n<br />\n第二 點解你需要6月5日就拎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T16:11:58.000Z","msg":"1. 比五馬分屍更勁。連個著制服既職員都示意唔洗再砌返完整出黎，但我有keep 起晒所有碎片比佢地。<br />\n<br />\n2. 返新工，新工要用passport 但未有新contract prove 自己要趕住用。"},{"pid":"d936f4e2628c6f70e8bdb4bf2df91541a39392de","tid":1149373,"uid":205193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34a4c610bd026b7c890905fe482714f1a6540344","tid":1149373,"uid":44512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"017cafc9547e4aa3fc2d01c1950ce095328e95